Get a table of all available roxygen2 tag labels

Source: R/pkgsnip.gen.R
roxy_labels.Rd

Returns a tibble listing all parameter labels included in this package, together with their name which can be provided as the name argument of param_label() or return_label().

roxy_labels(type = c("any", "param", "return", NA_character_))

roxy_lbls(type = c("any", "param", "return", NA_character_))

Arguments

type

The label type to return. A character scalar.

Value

A tibble.

Details

Currently, parameter labels with the following types and names are available:
